title: List of top 10 singles in 2019 (France)
text:
This is a list of <a href="single%20%28music%29">singles</a> that have peaked in the top 10 of the <a href="French%20Singles%20Chart">French Singles Chart</a> in 2019. 80 singles were in the Top 10 this year which 10 were on the number-one spot.
Entries by artists.
The following table shows artists who achieved two or more top 10 entries in 2019. The figures include both main artists and featured artists and the peak position in brackets.
